name: Basil Garlic Brschetta
desc: Crisp toasted slices of baguette topped with garlic, tomatoes, basil, a drizzle of olive oil, and a hint of sea salt.

name: Spicy Cauliflower Bites
desc: Crispy cauliflower florets tossed in a spicy buffalo sauce, served with a side of cooling ranch dip.

name: Caprese Salad Skewers
desc: Fresh mozzarella, cherry tomatoes, and basil leaves drizzled with balsamic glaze.

name: Hot Spiced Chai Latte
desc: A warm and comforting blend of black tea, aromatic spices, steamed milk, and a touch of honey or sugar.

desc: Warm chocolate cake with a gooey molten center, served with vanilla ice cream and strawberries.

name: Classic Tiramisu
desc: Traditional Italian dessert with layers of coffee-soaked ladyfingers and mascarpone cream.

name: Midnight Espresso Duo
desc: A bold blend of dark roast espresso paired with a velvety chocolate mousse.

desc: A warm seasonal fruit crumble served with a scoop of vanilla ice cream.

desc: A refreshing blend of zesty lemon and cool mint.

desc: Fresh raspberries muddled with lemon juice, simple syrup, and sparkling water. Served over ice with raspberries.

name: Vanilla Bean Panna Cotta with Berry Compote
desc: Creamy vanilla bean panna cotta served with a tangy berry compote.

name: Ribeye Steak

name: Iced Cold Brew Coffee with Vanilla Cream
desc: Rich cold brew coffee blended with vanilla cream and served over ice.
